---
title: Haloumi & Fluffy Veggie Couscous with Roasted Almonds & Yoghurt
description: Wipe up a haloumi and couscous extravaganza in four easy steps. Drizzle over some honey to coat the haloumi and
toss the couscous with some carrot and capsicum and it will look and taste like you’ve been cooking for hours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/651d7e19a19829649acd92b9-154097f3.jpeg
